    {
        "content": "<p>I think yes - I'm now formalizing some geometry, and now the F can be \"colinear\", \"area of triangle\", \"diameter of triangle\", and loads of things.<br>\nDo you mean that I should write the tactic by myself if necessary? If so, I'll learn it now.</p>",
